summary: This code is for the TCScore class, which is a part of the SMG_NothingIsAll project. It contains methods to calculate and get a comprehensive score from other modules such as TC and TOQueue. The class also has a method to derive a score dictionary using arrays of foModels and a mutable dictionary.
